casebody.head_matter:
In Re GRAND JURY SUBPOENA, applicant.
No. 18A669.
Supreme Court of the United States
Jan. 8, 2019.
Application for stay presented to THE CHIEF JUSTICE and by him referred to the Court denied. The administrative stay previously entered by THE CHIEF JUSTICE is vacated.
